## Prerequisites

{% if has_python %}
### Python — [PyPI](https://pypi.org/)

- Python {{ python_version }}: `pacman -S python`
- uv: `pacman -S uv`
- ruff: `pacman -S ruff`
{% if python_scaffolding == 'application' %}- mypy: `pacman -S mypy`
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% if has_node %}
### Node.js — [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/)

- Node.js {{ node_version }}: `pacman -S nodejs`
- {{ node_package_manager }}: `pacman -S {{ node_package_manager }}`
- Deno: `pacman -S deno`

{% endif %}
{% if has_go %}
### Go — [pkg.go.dev](https://pkg.go.dev/)

- Go {{ go_directive }}: `pacman -S go`
- golangci-lint: `pacman -S golangci-lint`
- gosec: `go install github.com/securego/gosec/v2/cmd/gosec@v2`
- govulncheck: `go tool govulncheck` (built into Go 1.24+)

{% endif %}
{% if has_rust %}
### Rust — [crates.io](https://crates.io/)

- Rust {{ rust_version }}: `pacman -S rustup` then `rustup toolchain install {{ rust_version }}`

{% endif %}
{% if has_dotnet %}
### .NET — [NuGet](https://www.nuget.org/)

- .NET SDK {{ dotnet_sdk_version }}: `pacman -S dotnet-sdk`

{% endif %}
{% if has_tofu %}
### OpenTofu — [OpenTofu Registry](https://search.opentofu.org/)

- OpenTofu {{ tofu_version }}: `pacman -S opentofu`
- tflint: `pacman -S tflint`
- terraform-docs: `yay -S terraform-docs`

{% endif %}
### Universal tools

{% if use_precommit %}- pre-commit: `pacman -S pre-commit`
- gitleaks: `pacman -S gitleaks`
{% if use_commitizen %}- commitizen: `yay -S python-commitizen`
{% endif %}{% endif %}{% if include_shell_tooling %}- shellcheck: `pacman -S shellcheck`
{% endif %}- yamlfmt: `pacman -S yamlfmt`
- rumdl: `pacman -S rumdl`
